name: FortiGate
description: The Sumo Logic App for FortiGate analyzes logs collected from your FortiGate UTM

panels.name: Connections Over Time
panels.queryString:
_sourcecategory=$$Foritgate "type=traffic" AND ("status=accept" OR "status=deny")
| parse "status=* " as action | parse "srcip=* " as srcip | parse "dstip=* " as dstip
| where action="accept" or action="deny"
| if ((srcip matches "10.*") OR (srcip matches "172.[16-31].*") OR (srcip matches "192.168.*"), 1, 0 ) as outbound
| if (outbound == "0", 1, 0) as inbound
| if (action="deny", 1, 0) as denied
| timeslice 5m
| sum(inbound) as inbound, sum(outbound) as outbound, sum(denied) as denied by _timeslice
| sort by _timeslice asc

panels.name: Denied Connections by Location
panels.queryString:
_sourcecategory=$$Foritgate "type=traffic" AND "status=deny" | extract "dstip=(?<dstip>.*?) " 
| where !(dstip matches "10.*") OR !(dstip matches "172.[16-31].*") OR !(dstip matches "192.168.*")
| lookup latitude, longitude, country_code, country_name, region, city, postal_code, area_code, metro_code from geo://default on ip = dstip
| where country_name !="" AND !isNull(country_name) 
| count by latitude, longitude, country_code, country_name, region, city, postal_code, area_code, metro_code

panels.name: Outbound Connections Over Time
panels.queryString:
_sourcecategory=$$Foritgate "type=traffic" | extract "dstip=(?<dstip>.*?) " 
| where !(dstip matches "10.*" OR dstip matches "172.16.*" OR dstip matches "192.168.*")
| lookup latitude, longitude, country_code, country_name, region, city, postal_code, area_code, metro_code from geo://default on ip = dstip
| timeslice 5m
| count by _timeslice,country_name
| transpose row _timeslice column country_name as *

panels.name: Outbound Destinations
panels.queryString:
_sourcecategory=$$Foritgate "type=traffic" AND dstip* | extract "dstip=(?<dstip>.*?) " 
| where !(dstip matches "10.*") OR !(dstip matches "172.[16-31].*") OR !(dstip matches "192.168.*")
| lookup latitude, longitude, country_code, country_name, region, city, postal_code, area_code, metro_code from geo://default on ip = dstip
| count by latitude, longitude, country_code, country_name, region, city, postal_code, area_code, metro_code

panels.name: Top Denied Sources
panels.queryString:
_sourcecategory=$$Foritgate "type=traffic" AND "status=deny" | extract "srcip=(?<srcip>.*?) " 
| count as count srcip 
| sort by count 
| limit 10

panels.name: Most Severe Messages
panels.queryString:
_sourcecategory=$$Foritgate !%ASA
| parse "level=* " as Severity nodrop
| parse "logid=* " as logID nodrop
| parse "action=* " as action nodrop
| parse "status=* " as status nodrop
| parse "reason=\"*\"" as reason nodrop
| WHERE Severity <> "information"
| count as count by severity, action, status, reason
| sort count
| limit 5

panels.name: Protocol Distribution Over Time
panels.queryString:
_sourcecategory=$$Foritgate "type=traffic" AND "status=deny" AND proto*
| extract "proto=(?<proto>.*?) " 
| if (proto matches "1", "ICMP", proto) as protocol
| if (proto matches "6", "TCP", protocol) as protocol
| if (proto matches "17", "UDP", protocol) as protocol
| if (proto matches "50", "IPSEC-ESP", protocol) as protocol
| if (proto matches "51", "IPSEC-AH", protocol) as protocol
| if (!(proto == "1" OR proto == "6" OR proto == "17" OR proto == "50" OR proto == "51"), "OTHER", protocol) as protocol
| timeslice by 5m
| count by _timeslice, protocol
| transpose row _timeslice column protocol as *

panels.name: Bandwidth Served in MBytes
panels.queryString:
_sourcecategory=$$Foritgate "type=traffic"
| parse "sentbyte=* " as bsnt | parse "rcvdbyte=* " as brec
| brec+bsnt as bTot
| timeslice 5m
| sum(btot) as bytes by _timeslice,_sourceHost
| (bytes/1000000) as mbytes
| fields - bytes
| transpose row _timeslice column _sourceHost as *

panels.name: Outbound Connections To High Risk Countries
panels.queryString:
_sourcecategory=$$Foritgate "type=traffic" AND dstip* | extract "dstip=(?<dstip>.*?) "
| where !(dstip matches "10.*") OR !(dstip matches "172.16.*") OR !(dstip matches "192.168.*")
| lookup latitude, longitude, country_code, country_name, region, city, postal_code, area_code, metro_code from geo://default on ip = dstip
| where country_name in ("Thailand","Indonesia","Vietnam","Saudi Arabia","China","Russian Federation","Philippines","South Africa")
| timeslice 5m
| count by _timeslice,country_name
| transpose row _timeslice column country_name as *

children.name: Fortigate Event Parser
children.searchQuery:
_sourcecategory=$$Foritgate !(%ASA) "type=event"
| extract "date=(?<date>.*?) time=(?<time>.*?) devname=(?<devname>.*?) devid=(?<devid>.*?) logid=(?<logid>.*?) type=(?<type>.*?) subtype=(?<subtype>.*?) (?:eventtype=(?<eventtype>.*?) )?level=(?<level>.*?) vd=[\"]*(?<vd>.*?)[\"]* "

children.name: FortiGate Traffic Parser
children.searchQuery:
_sourcecategory=$$Foritgate !%ASA "type=traffic"
| extract "date=(?<date>.*?) time=(?<time>.*?) devname=(?<devname>.*?) devid=(?<devid>.*?) logid=(?<logid>.*?) type=(?<type>.*?) subtype=(?<subtype>.*?) level=(?<level>.*?) vd=[\"]*(?<vd>.*?)[\"]* " nodrop
| extract "srcip=(?<srcip>.*?) (?:srcport=(?<srcport>.*?) )?(?:srcintf=[\"]*(?<srcintf>.*?)[\"]*)? dstip=(?<dstip>.*?) (?:dstport=(?<dstport>.*?) )?(?:dstintf=[\"]*(?<dstintf>.*?)[\"]*)? " nodrop
| extract "(?:poluuid=(?<poluuid>.*?) )?sessionid=(?<sessionid>.*?) action=(?<action>.*?) policyid=(?<policyid>.*?) (?:dstcountry=\"(?<dstcountry>.*?)\" srccountry=\"(?<srccountry>.*?)\"\s)?" nodrop
| extract "trandisp=(?<trandisp>.*?) service=(?<service>.*?) proto=(?<proto>.*?) " nodrop
| extract "(?:appid=(?<appid>.*?) app=\"(?<app>.*?)\" appcat=\"(?<appcat>.*?)\" apprisk=(?<apprisk>.*?) )?applist=\"(?<applist>.*?)\" (?:appact=(?<appact>.*?) )?" nodrop
| extract "duration=(?<duration>.*?) sentbyte=(?<sentbyte>.*?) rcvdbyte=(?<rcvdbyte>.*?) (?:sentpkt=(?<sentpkt>.*?) rcvdpkt=(?<rcvdpkt>.*?)[\s$])?" nodrop
| extract "utmaction=(?<utmaction>.*?) (?:countweb=(?<countweb>.*?)[\s$]+)?(?:countapp=(?<countapp>.*?)[\s$]+)?" nodrop //[\s$]+
| extract "crscore=(?<crscore>.*?) craction=(?<craction>.*?)$" nodrop

children.name: FortiGate UTM Parser
children.searchQuery:
_sourcecategory=$$Foritgate !(%ASA) "type=utm"
| extract "date=(?<date>.*?) time=(?<time>.*?) devname=(?<devname>.*?) devid=(?<devid>.*?) logid=(?<logid>.*?) type=(?<type>.*?) subtype=(?<subtype>.*?) eventtype=(?<eventtype>.*?) level=(?<level>.*?) vd=[\"]*(?<vd>.*?)[\"]* " nodrop
| extract "sessionid=(?<sessionid>.*?) srcip=(?<srcip>.*?) srcport=(?<srcport>.*?) dstip=(?<dstip>.*?) dstport=(?<dstport>.*?) service=(?<service>.*?) profile=\"(?<profile>.*?)\" action=(?<action>.*?) reqtype=(?<reqtype>.*?) msg=\"(?<msg>.*?)\" sentbyte=(?<sentbyte>.*?) rcvdbyte=(?<rcvdbyte>.*?)" nodrop
| extract "sessionid=(?<sessionid>.*?) srcip=(?<srcip>.*?) srcport=(?<srcport>.*?) dstip=(?<dstip>.*?) dstport=(?<dstport>.*?) proto=(?<proto>.*?) service=(?<service>.*?) hostname=\"(?<hostname>.*?)\" profile=\"(?<profile>.*?)\" action=(?<action>.*?) reqtype=(?<reqtype>.*?) url=\"(?<url>.*?)\" sentbyte=(?<sentbyte>.*?) rcvdbyte=(?<rcvdbyte>.*?) direction=(?<direction>.*?) msg=\"(?<msg>.*?)\" method=(?<method>.*?) cat=(?<cat>.*?) catdesc=\"(?<catdesc>.*?)\"$" nodrop
| extract "appid=(?<appid>.*?) srcip=(?<srcip>.*?) srcport=(?<srcport>.*?) dstip=(?<dstip>.*?) dstport=(?<dstport>.*?) proto=(?<proto>.*?) service=(?<service>.*?) sessionid=(?<sessionid>.*?) applist=\"(?<applist>.*?)\" appcat=\"(?<appcat>.*?)\" app=\"(?<app>.*?)\" action=(?<action>.*?) (?:hostname=\"(?<hostname>.*?)\" url=\"(?<url>.*?)\" )?msg=\"(?<msg>.*?)\" apprisk=(?<apprisk>.*?)$" nodrop
//| count by sessionid,srcip,srcport,dstip,dstport,proto,service,hostname,profile,action,reqtype,url,sentbyte,rcvdbyte,direction,msg,method,cat,catdesc,appid,applist,appcat,app,apprisk
